\par 
\par      Silents Under the Stars is a key
 support event for the Friends of Hart Park.  Net profits from the program help underwrite a number of annual activities, and, in addition, enable the Friends to consider and inaugurate new outreach.  Financial assistance from Los Angeles County is minima
