art Hall there have been suggestions about moving the supper and film program to the lower park, with its easy accessibility to parking and the possibility of a larger audience.  However, support persists for keeping the Silents at its now-traditional loc
ation, high on }{\f1\fs20\ul\insrsid15741021 La Loma:}{\f1\fs20\insrsid15741021 
